text.tspan: more or less the same as 2N3904
Observe the voltage divider on the outputs.
This divider with 1k8 and 1k gives less than
5v on the output. That might be too little
for many of the modules built i MiaW (and
other modules too) Maybe change 1k8 to 1k
Also note that all outputs /2-/128 are inverted to /1,
as all divisions happen on the falling edge of /1.
Some alterations have been done to the original design to add /1 and step pushbutton.
